{# Reusable Delete Confirmation Modal #}
<div id="deleteModal" class="fixed inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-50 hidden items-center justify-center z-50">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 max-w-md w-full mx-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-600 mb-4">Usuń wydatek</h2>

        <div class="mb-6">
            <p class="text-lg mb-4">Czy na pewno chcesz usunąć ten wydatek?</p>

            <div class="recurring-warning bg-yellow-100 border border-yellow-400 text-yellow-700 px-4 py-3 rounded mb-4" style="display: none;">
                <strong>⚠️ Uwaga:</strong> To jest wydatek cykliczny.
                Usunięcie tej wystąpienia nie wpłynie na inne wystąpienia.
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded">
                <p><strong class="expense-name">Nazwa wydatku</strong></p>
                <p class="expense-amount">Kwota: 0.00 zł</p>
                <p class="expense-date">Data: 01.01.2024</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex space-x-4 justify-end">
            <button type="button" onclick="hideDeleteConfirm()"
                    class="px-6 py-3 bg-gray-300 text-gray-700 font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-400">
                Anuluj
            </button>
            <button type="button" onclick="confirmDelete()"
                    class="px-6 py-3 bg-red-600 text-white font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-red-800">
                Tak, usuń
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
